         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">7/8/90 ¶  ¶ In 1888, esteemed Mr Tepper, you sent me a plant from moist places near the mouth of the Murray River, ¶  that I determined after a hasty look as a  ¶ Scleranthus ¶ . It was numbered 5. I ...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">90.08.07</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">To Otto Tepper</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">RB MSS M198, Library, Royal Botanic Gardens Melbourne.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">7/8/90</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Im Jahre 1888, geehrter Herr Tepper, sandten Sie mir eine Pflanze von feuchten Plätzen nahe der Mündung des Murray-Flusses, welche ich nach hastigem Besehen als einen <name key="Scleranthus">Scleranthus</name> bezeichnete. Sie war 5 numerirt. Ich sehe jetzt dass es die var. caespitosa von Stellaria palustris ist.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">Sie ehrende der Ihre</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">7/8/90</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>In 1888, esteemed Mr Tepper, you sent me a plant from moist places near the mouth of the Murray River,<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">SA.</p>
               </note> that I determined after a hasty look as a <seg style="font-style: italic; ">
                  <name key="Scleranthus">Scleranthus</name>
               </seg>. It was numbered 5. I now see that it is the variety <seg style="font-style: italic; ">caespitosa</seg> of <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Stellaria palustris</seg>.<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">In B89.05.03, p. 5, M recognised <seg style="font-style: italic; ">S. palustris</seg> as an earlier name of <seg style="font-style: italic; ">S. glauca</seg>, listed in Bentham (1863-78), vol. 1, p. 158, where Bentham also listed the variety <seg style="font-style: italic; ">caespitosa</seg>. See also B88.11.02, p. 166. The earliest formal combination for <seg style="font-style: italic; ">S. palustris</seg> var <seg style="font-style: italic; ">caespitosa</seg> listed by APNI (accessed 27 November 2020) is in J. Black (1922-9), p. 231.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Respectfully your</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Scleranthus">Scleranthus</name>
            </p>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">Stellaria palustris <seg style="font-style: normal; ">var</seg> caespitosa</p>
